  "texts": [
    "In the longevity community, the widespread popularity of supplements raises similar concerns, as their excessive or unregulated use can lead to cross-reactions and cumulative toxicities.",
    "Decagon is a tool that uses graph convolutional neural networks to analyze multimodal graphs, integrating protein-protein and drug-protein interactions [132].",
    "It predicts the occurrence of a side effect from a drug combination and identifies the specific type of side effect.As the number of identified geroprotectors continued to grow, the need for a comprehensive database became increasingly evident.",
    "In 2015, the first geroprotector database \"geroprotectors.org\" was established, featuring 250 experiments covering over 200 known or candidate geroprotectors [133].",
    "In March 2024, this database contained 2408 references for geroprotective compounds."
  ],
